1 0 0 1 54 528 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 514 Tm (### 1\) Hardcoded Administrative Credentials in Client) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 500 Tm (- Vulnerability name: Hardcoded Credentials \(CWE-798\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 486 Tm (- Severity: Critical) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 472 Tm (- Risk:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 458 Tm (  - Admin credentials were embedded in frontend code \(`admin` / `password`\).) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 444 Tm (  - Any user inspecting JS could obtain admin access.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 430 Tm (- Evidence before fix:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 416 Tm (  - `client/src/pages/AdminLogin.jsx` validated static username/password directly in browser) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 402 Tm (logic.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 388 Tm (- Fix implemented:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 374 Tm (  - Removed hardcoded credential checks from client.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 360 Tm (  - Added server-side authentication endpoint `POST /api/admin/login`.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 346 Tm (  - Client now submits credentials to server; server returns signed admin token only on) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 332 Tm (successful validation.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 318 Tm (- Files changed:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 304 Tm (  - `client/src/pages/AdminLogin.jsx`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 290 Tm (  - `server/index.js`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 276 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 262 Tm (### 2\) Missing Server-Side Authorization on Admin Endpoints) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 248 Tm (- Vulnerability name: Broken Access Control \(OWASP A01:2021\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 234 Tm (- Severity: Critical) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 220 Tm (- Risk:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 206 Tm (  - Sensitive write operations were callable without verified admin identity.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 192 Tm (  - Attackers could modify course/content/analytics data.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 178 Tm (- Affected endpoints fixed:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 164 Tm (  - `POST /api/courses`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 150 Tm (  - `PUT /api/courses/:id`) Tj
