1 0 0 1 54 430 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 416 Tm (### 4\) Insecure Admin Session Trust \(Client-Only Flag\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 402 Tm (- Vulnerability name: Improper Authentication / Client-Side Trust of Security State) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 388 Tm (- Severity: High) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 374 Tm (- Risk:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 360 Tm (  - Route guard trusted `localStorage.adminAuth === 'true'` alone.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 346 Tm (  - Local flag tampering could unlock admin UI flow.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 332 Tm (- Fix implemented:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 318 Tm (  - Client admin guard now requires both:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 304 Tm (    - `adminAuth === 'true'`) Tj
