1 0 0 1 54 738 Tm (  - `server/index.js`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 724 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 710 Tm (## Security Controls Added) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 696 Tm (- HMAC-signed admin token generation and verification.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 682 Tm (- Expiration support for admin tokens \(`ADMIN_TOKEN_TTL_SECONDS`\).) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 668 Tm (- Constant-time credential comparison \(`timingSafeEqual`\) to reduce timing leakage.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 654 Tm (- Centralized admin auth helper propagation on frontend API layer.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 640 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 626 Tm (## Environment Variables Required) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 612 Tm (- `ADMIN_USER`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 598 Tm (- `ADMIN_PASSWORD`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 584 Tm (- `ADMIN_TOKEN_SECRET`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 570 Tm (- `ALLOWED_ORIGINS`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 556 Tm (- Optional: `ADMIN_TOKEN_TTL_SECONDS`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 542 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 528 Tm (## Residual Risks \(Not Yet Remediated\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 514 Tm (1. Learner authentication is still localStorage-driven and not server-validated.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 500 Tm (2. Certificate list endpoint by email \(`/api/certificates?email=...`\) can still allow) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 486 Tm (enumeration/privacy risk without user-bound auth.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 472 Tm (3. No rate limiting/lockout on admin login endpoint.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 458 Tm (4. No CSRF design review for future cookie-based auth migration.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 444 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 430 Tm (## Recommended Next Phase) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 416 Tm (1. Implement proper learner JWT/session auth and server-side authorization checks.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 402 Tm (2. Lock certificate access to authenticated user identity \(token subject\), not email query) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 388 Tm (alone.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 374 Tm (3. Add rate limiting and login attempt controls on `/api/admin/login` and sensitive endpoints.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 360 Tm (4. Add security headers \(`helmet`\) and centralized audit logging.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 346 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 332 Tm (## Verification Summary) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 318 Tm (- Static syntax checks passed for modified server files via Node check.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 304 Tm (- Admin flow updated end-to-end: login -> token storage -> protected route -> authenticated) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 290 Tm (admin API calls.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 276 Tm (- Sensitive admin endpoints now reject unauthorized requests with `401 Unauthorized`.) Tj
ET
